---
import MkcLayout from '../layouts/MkcLayout.astro';
---

<MkcLayout title="Classifiche | Matenano Kings Cup">
  <section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="w-full max-w-4xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900/50 filter blur-[8px] transform -skew-y-3">
        <div class="h-12 border-b border-white/10"></div>
        <div class="h-16 border-b border-white/5"></div>
        <div class="h-16 border-b border-white/5"></div>
        <div class="h-16 border-b border-white/5"></div>
        <div class="h-16"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <span data-aos="fade-down" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/10 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-400 mb-8">
        ⏳ In Attesa del Sorteggio
      </span>
      
      <h1 data-aos="fade-up" class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-white uppercase mb-6">
        Gironi &<br />Classifiche
      </h1>
      
      <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="space-y-6 text-zinc-300 font-light text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto p-8 rounded-3xl bg-black/60 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-2xl">
        <p>
          Questa sezione ospiterà il cuore pulsante della competizione: i punteggi, la differenza reti, i cartellini e le statistiche dei marcatori in tempo reale.
        </p>
        <p>
          Le classifiche sono temporaneamente bloccate in attesa del termine delle iscrizioni. Una volta definito il numero dei team, procederemo con il <strong class="text-white">sorteggio ufficiale dei gironi</strong> e la piattaforma prenderà vita, registrando ogni singola vittoria sul campo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="mt-10">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-amber-400 text-black rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(251,191,36,0.2)]">
          Torna alla Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MkcLayout>